title: Dave Doeren breaks down how NC State rookies will fare in NFL (Football 08/09)
description:
Will Brinson chats up NC State head coach Dave Doeren to find out how his seven former players taken in the 2018 NFL Draft will fare with their respective teams in the NFL, and they also run through some of his current players and how they'll fit at the next level, including quarterback Ryan Finley. Will also breaks down the latest NFL news and notes from around the league.
